orm into a beast of CR 1 or less for 7 hours, They revert if they fall unconcious or reach 0 hp. The Elite retains his intelligence, Charisma, and wisdom and other abilities but loses the ability to cast spells, though he may continue to Concentrate on a spell he has already cast. The elite may only speak or use his hands if his beast form allows him to do so. The rest of his stats and abilities are replaced with the beast's. His equipment merges with his new form\n\nAlternately the Elite can use this feature to gain 30 temporary hit points, doubles the damage of his Memory of roots feature, his melee attacks deal 1d6 poison damage to any target they hit. These benefits last or ten minutes","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"The God King's Command","Description":"Any humanoid slain by the Elite's Memory of Roots feature rises as a zombie with 1 hit point at the end of his turn and takes his turn immediately after the elite's. It can only attack and remains animate for 1 hour, after which it collapses and dies","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0}],"_Actions":[{"Title":"Shillelagh","Description":null,"isDamage":true,"isSpell":false,"attack":{"_Attack":"Melee Spell Attack","Bonus":"10","Reach":5,"RangeClose":0,"RangeFar":0,"Target":"one creature","HitDiceNumber":3,"HitDiceSize":8,"HitDamageBonus":5,"HitAverageDamage":18,"HitText":"","HitDamageType":"Bludgeoning"},"saveDC":0}],"_Reactions":[],"_Legendaries":[],"_advancedSpells":[],"_advancedSpellData":[],"Title":"","STR":8,"DEX":15,"CON":14,"INT":14,"WIS":19,"CHA":10,"proficency":4,"Speed":"30 ft.","AC":"17 (Kholirahi root magic)","HP":"65 (10d8 + 20)","CR":{"Index":13,"CR":"10","profBonus":4,"ArmorClass":17,"AttackBonus":7,"SaveDC":16,"LowHP":206,"HighHP":220,"XP":5900},"CreatureName":"Kholirahi Elite","CreatureSize":"Tiny","CreatureType":"Humanoid","CreatureAlign":"Unaligned","unique":false,"CreatureGender":"Male","LegendaryActions":"3"}